data.description: Beautiful Barndominium on 4.5 acres in Somervell County. Wide open floorplan as you walk in the front door. Perfect for family gatherings and entertaining. Plenty of covered parking with a 2 car garage and 2 additional carports. Amazing sunset views on a quiet country road. Enjoy country life just minutes from Glen Rose. Easy commute to Stephenville, Granbury, Cleburne, and Fort Worth.
